title: Sample RFI for Furniture
additional_fields: What is the lead time for production?
Can you provide custom packaging options?
What are the material specifications?
Do you offer any discounts for bulk orders?
What is your MOQ (Minimum Order Quantity)?
information: Looking for a supplier for custom-made office furniture. Must comply with ISO quality standards.
comment: Please prioritize suppliers with experience in exporting to Europe.

title: RFI for PCB Manufacturing
additional_fields: What is your PCB layer count capability?
Can you meet RoHS compliance?
Do you provide engineering support during production?
What is the standard testing procedure for PCBs?
Can you provide references from previous clients?
information: Seeking a reliable manufacturer for multi-layer PCBs used in industrial control systems.
comment: Looking for a long-term partnership with high-quality and fast turnaround.

title: RFI for Organic Cotton T-Shirt Production
additional_fields: Do you source GOTS-certified organic cotton?
Can you handle custom dyeing and labeling?
What are the available fabric weights?
What is your standard packaging?
Can you provide sustainable packaging solutions?
information: Looking for a supplier to produce organic cotton T-shirts for a new eco-friendly fashion line.
comment: Prefer suppliers with experience working with European fashion brands.

title: RFI for Automotive Brake Pad Suppliers
additional_fields: What materials are used in your brake pads?
What are your quality assurance processes?
Can you meet ISO/TS 16949 certification?
Do you offer custom branding on the brake pads?
What are your warranty policies?
information: We are looking for brake pad suppliers for aftermarket automotive applications, focusing on quality and durability.
comment: Preference given to suppliers with previous experience in the North American market.

title: RFI for Custom Eco-Friendly Packaging
additional_fields: Do you offer biodegradable packaging materials?
Can you customize packaging sizes and shapes?
What is your production lead time?
Can you provide design support for the packaging?
Are your materials recyclable or compostable?
information: Seeking eco-friendly packaging solutions for a new line of organic skincare products.
comment: Looking for innovative and sustainable packaging options to reduce carbon footprint.

title: RFI for Sustainable Building Materials
additional_fields: Do you offer recycled materials for construction?
What certifications do your materials hold (LEED, BREEAM, etc.)?

information: We are looking for suppliers of sustainable building materials for a green construction project.
comment: Priority given to suppliers with proven environmental certifications and compliance.
